        "en_title": "Media, '7 children killed by ordigno in southern Syria'",
        "en_content": "Seven children were killed\nin the explosion of a garden in the countryside of Daraa, in the south\nSyria, close to borders with Jordan, Lebanon and\nIsrael. The state media cited by Al Arabiya refer it.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
