        "filename": "ner_conc_en_2024-04-07T00.00.24E1712448024.915664.json",
        "en_title": "Exit-poll, the Western Korcok wins in Slovakia",
        "en_content": "At least second exit-poll\non behalf of the Slovak public television,\nwinner of the presidential election ballot\nSlovakia would be the pro-Western diplomat Ivan Korcok,\nwith 51.1% of the votes.\n\n\nPeter Pellegrini, President of the Allied Parliament of the\npro-Russian populist premier Robert Fico, would get the\n48.9 % of consents. The exit-poll result was\nrelaunched by TV \"Ta3\".\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
