        "filename": "ner_conc_en_2024-04-07T00.00.24E1712448024.915664.json",
        "en_title": "Use warn, from China geospatial intelligence to Moscow",
        "en_content": "The United States put in\nguard the allies on the fact that China is stepping up\nits support to Russia by providing, among other things, intelligence\ngeospatial to help Moscow in its war against Ukraine.\n\n\nThe Bloomberg agency reports it citing some sources, according to the\nwhich China supplied Russia satellite images for\nmilitary purposes.\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
